      "title": "113 people infected with Corona have been identified",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Another 113 people infected with corona have been identified in the country yesterday (31).",
        "This information has been given in an updated report issued by the Department of Epidemiology of the Ministry of Health.",
        "The total number of confirmed cases of corona infection in the country has increased to 665,739. (a)"
